WEBVTT

00:02.141 --> 00:03.659
<i>Previously on Medium...</i>

00:03.859 --> 00:06.159
What's the matter Mr. Good,

00:06.250 --> 00:07.784
can't sleep?

00:07.852 --> 00:09.419
You know, he's haunting you.

00:09.487 --> 00:12.055
If anyone deserves
to be haunted...

00:12.123 --> 00:13.590
You've done nothing
to deserve this.

00:13.658 --> 00:15.992
Well, I always just kind of
assumed you knew.

00:16.059 --> 00:17.827
Knew what? Do you remember
that night you dreamed

00:17.895 --> 00:19.362
<i>that lady was</i>
<i>gonna kill my brother,</i>

00:19.430 --> 00:20.764
<i>you called me to warn me,</i>

00:20.831 --> 00:23.567
I told you that it was too late,
it'd already happened?

00:24.335 --> 00:25.735
I lied.

00:25.803 --> 00:27.971
Oh, my God.

00:28.039 --> 00:29.839
You let him die.

00:29.907 --> 00:31.808
I'm fighting for my life
here, Allison,

00:31.876 --> 00:34.110
for my job, for my future.

00:34.178 --> 00:36.680
I think you'll get back
everything you started with,

00:36.747 --> 00:38.315
except for my friendship.

