00:59.170 --> 01:00.770
Lee, are you here?

01:00.838 --> 01:02.439
Do you have the baby?

01:02.506 --> 01:04.774
Yeah, I got her.
I'm in the kitchen.

01:09.146 --> 01:10.247
Hi.

01:10.314 --> 01:12.082
Oh, what happened?

01:12.149 --> 01:14.451
Did you wake up hungry
and Mommy not here?

01:14.518 --> 01:16.920
Did Daddy give you a bottle?

01:16.988 --> 01:18.622
He didn't feed her;
I-I fed her.

01:18.689 --> 01:21.291
Who are you? What are
you doing in my home?

01:21.359 --> 01:24.194
Oh, I'm-I'm Paul,
Lee's older brother.

01:25.363 --> 01:26.796
Beautiful kid, yeah.

01:26.864 --> 01:29.466
I fed her, and she
gobbled it right up.

01:29.533 --> 01:30.700
It's not formula.

01:30.768 --> 01:32.569
Something better.

01:32.637 --> 01:34.237
Something I whipped up myself.

01:34.305 --> 01:36.473
What are you talking about?

01:36.540 --> 01:38.675
She doesn't eat solid food yet.

01:38.743 --> 01:40.944
Oh, I don't know,
she loved this.

01:41.012 --> 01:42.279
You want some?

01:42.346 --> 01:44.981
I put the leftovers
in the fridge.

01:57.928 --> 02:00.130
Oh...

02:00.197 --> 02:01.865
Lee, you okay?

02:01.932 --> 02:04.267
Yeah.

02:04.335 --> 02:07.370
Same thing.
I can't sleep.

02:07.438 --> 02:09.705
Nightmares,
nothing but nightmares.

02:09.774 --> 02:11.741
Lee, how long can this go on?

02:11.809 --> 02:13.510
I don't know
what to tell you.

02:13.577 --> 02:17.414
I've seen three doctors,
taken all kinds of pills.

02:20.151 --> 02:23.753
I want what you want--
I want to sleep.

02:23.821 --> 02:27.390
I want to get some rest.

02:27.458 --> 02:29.459
Oh...

02:33.864 --> 02:37.000
Hey, I'm sorry,
Mr. Good, Mrs. Good,

02:37.068 --> 02:39.569
Baby Good.

02:39.637 --> 02:41.805
Am I keeping you up?

02:42.973 --> 02:44.874
Well, don't worry,

02:44.942 --> 02:48.278
it's a short-term problem.

02:48.346 --> 02:50.747
The dead don't sleep.

